│ reinserting instructions, which skips dropping references and scanning users for those instructions. I will     │
│ remove that `continue;` within the destructor so the reinserted instructions are cleaned up. To further ensure  │
│ deletability, I will also insert a trivial-users cleanup loop just before `dropAllReferences()` so              │
│ trivially-dead users are collected and removed later. This preserves assertions and IR semantics.               │
│                                                                                                                 │
│ ```bash                                                                                                         │
│ awk '                                                                                                           │
