│ - Rebuild the destructor to insert temporarily parent-less instructions back to a block (no early continue).    │
│ - Collect trivially-dead producers feeding each candidate.                                                      │
│ - Only call dropAllReferences and schedule erase for instructions that are use_empty.                           │
│ - Erase only those scheduled (ToErase), preserving the original assert.                                         │
│ - Finally, DCE the trivially-dead producers.                                                                    │
│ This ensures we never leave instructions with null operands in IR and avoids the assertion for live             │
│ instructions.                                                                                                   │
